(‘integrity and confidentiality’) .\n\nThe controller shall be responsible for, and be able to demonstrate compliance with, paragraph 1 (‘accountability’) .	5	{"extracted_at": "2025-02-08T13:11:20.931585", "is_definitions": false}	2025-02-08 21:11:21.08534+00	2025-02-08 21:11:21.08534+00
