sis of a service contract.\n\nThe controller or the processor shall publish the contact details of the data protection officer and communicate them to the supervisory authority.	37	{"extracted_at": "2025-02-08T13:11:20.966657", "is_definitions": false}	2025-02-08 21:11:21.08534+00	2025-02-08 21:11:21.08534+00
