or of the controller or processor for the cross-border processing carried out by that controller or processor.	56	{"extracted_at": "2025-02-08T13:11:20.979632", "is_definitions": false}	2025-02-08 21:11:21.08534+00	2025-02-08 21:11:21.08534+00
