rred to in paragraphs 2 and 3 serves at the same time another purpose, the derogations shall apply only to processing for the purposes referred to in those paragraphs.	89	{"extracted_at": "2025-02-08T13:11:20.998909", "is_definitions": false}	2025-02-08 21:11:21.08534+00	2025-02-08 21:11:21.08534+00
