352bb2a7-1c36-4671-80ef-1b9400e21eac	b1c40c9d-ef46-45c5-98fe-7fb62fc34d1d	chapeau	\N	For the processing of personal data by the Union institutions, bodies, offices and agencies, Regulation (EC) No 45/2001 applies. Regulation (EC) No 45/2001 and other Union legal acts applicable to such processing of personal data shall be adapted to the principles and rules of this Regulation in accordance with Article 98.	1
