2a534601-0288-4c1a-b3a5-6659a391caee	0e4ac2fb-38ab-46b9-9671-31cbc0cdfede	3	\N	The records referred to in paragraphs 1 and 2 shall be in writing, including in electronic form.	{"chapeau_count": 1, "total_elements": 1, "subparagraph_count": 0}	2025-02-08 21:11:21.08534+00	2025-02-08 21:11:21.08534+00
