e9cc5550-bf50-4cb9-ab2e-fa45e35abf16	1f2e8be4-e70a-4c06-b97b-25419cad14b5	1	\N	The discussions of the Board shall be confidential where the Board deems it necessary, as provided for in its rules of procedure.	{"chapeau_count": 1, "total_elements": 1, "subparagraph_count": 0}	2025-02-08 21:11:21.08534+00	2025-02-08 21:11:21.08534+00
