a9b4d540-0ef8-429b-9e52-fbcbc75fcc5c	8d104508-586e-4efd-b065-744c38bcb56a	2	\N	Without prejudice to any other administrative or non-judicial remedy, each data subject shall have the right to a an effective judicial remedy where the supervisory authority which is competent pursuant to Articles 55 and 56 does not handle a complaint or does not inform the data subject within three months on the progress or outcome of the complaint lodged pursuant to Article 77.	{"chapeau_count": 1, "total_elements": 1, "subparagraph_count": 0}	2025-02-08 21:11:21.08534+00	2025-02-08 21:11:21.08534+00
